cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.RO, cs.HC

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a visual odometry algorithm for processing video frames and creating a panoramic image mosaic. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is also likely as the paper discusses the display and visualization of the Swipe Mosaics. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is relevant as the paper deals with processing and displaying video frames. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is possible as the proposed algorithm could be used for robot navigation and mapping. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also possible as the Swipe Mosaics are presented as an interactive visualization for closer inspection of a scene.
